<HEAD>Poll Shows Bush, Dukakis Leading Their Parties In Florida</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MIAMI (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   With Super Tuesday just a week and half away, Vice
President George Bush and Massachusetts Gov. Michael Dukakis are
