<HEAD>GOP Senate Candidate Kicks Off Effort Against Lautenberg</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TINTON FALLS, N.J. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Former Army football star Peter
Dawkins today announced his candidacy for the GOP Senate nomination
